|WKBConstitution:                Range: |YKB1-300

    |YKOConstitution is a measure of physical toughness and stamina. High
constitution allows a player to perform strenuous tasks for a longer
time. It increases the amount of hit points the player has, and therefore
increases the amount of damage that can be taken before needing to rest
or heal. Your guild determines constitution's base hit-point multiplier.
That multiplier increases by one at levels 50, 100, 150, 200, and 250.
